pageContext.description: Dimensions: EL 36.5mm; EWe 38; EDs 4.5 (+?); Wt. 53 g,Manufacture: intact patina on side has no trace of cg. fl. - smooth; almost certainly had bevelled edge - uncertain how well-defined,Condition: break anc. - some crushing of body poss. associated with breaking; edge blunt and little irreg., no certain breaks,Attached Material: yellow-brown soil mainly in socket, incl. frag. of organic fibre - prob. incidental (eg. root)
